-- Reliance Steel to buy Illinois-based Clayton Metals
-- 
-- Wed Jun 20, 2007 9:36am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/20/us-claytonmetals-takeover-reliancesteel-idUSWNAS435620070620

 

 (Reuters) - Reliance Steel & Aluminum Co. ( RS.N ), a metals processor and products manufacturer, said it agreed to acquire Wood Dale, Illinois-based Clayton Metals Inc. for an undisclosed sum 

 Current management is expected to remain in place, the company said in a statement, adding that the deal is expected to be finalized within the next 30 days. Clayton Metals specializes in the processing and distribution of aluminum, stainless steel and red metal flat-rolled products, custom extrusions and aluminum circles, the company added. (Reporting by Shikhar Balwani in Bangalore)